@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<div class="container py-4">

    <div class="mb-4">
        <h1 class="h3 mb-1">Privacy Policy</h1>
        <div class="text-muted small">
            Digitalisation Manager – Archive Management System
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="card shadow-sm">
        <div class="card-body">

            <h2 class="h5">1. Purpose</h2>
            <p>
                This system is designed for the management and digitisation of archival materials.
                It stores metadata for Funds, Items, and associated digital TIFF files.
            </p>

            <h2 class="h5 mt-4">2. Authentication</h2>
            <p>
                Access to the application requires authentication.
                User accounts are managed through ASP.NET Core Identity.
                Only authorised users can create, edit, upload, or delete archive data.
            </p>

            <h2 class="h5 mt-4">3. Stored Data</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>Fund metadata</li>
                <li>Item metadata (inventory number, description, document date, status)</li>
                <li>Digital file metadata (original name, size, checksum, upload date)</li>
                <li>Uploaded TIFF files stored on disk</li>
            </ul>

            <h2 class="h5 mt-4">4. File Storage</h2>
            <p>
                Digital files are stored on the server file system in a structured directory:
            </p>

            <div class="bg-light border rounded p-2 small mb-3">
                Storage/Funds/{FundId}/Items/{ItemId}/Tiffs/{guid}.tif
            </div>

            <p>
                Files are not stored in the database.
                Access to files is controlled through authorised controller actions.
            </p>

            <h2 class="h5 mt-4">5. Data Protection</h2>
            <p>
                Uploaded files are validated for type and size.
                Each file is stored with a SHA-256 checksum for integrity verification.
            </p>

            <h2 class="h5 mt-4">6. Contact</h2>
            <p>
                For questions regarding data handling or system access,
                please contact the system administrator.
            </p>

        </div>
    </div>

</div>
